ecting an upper threshold for the number of active social contacts that\nindividuals maintain over the course of one week.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jun 2014 23:36:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Aug 2014 23:27:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
